These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
3 different games are played: domino, mah-jongg, backgammon
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, classical, house
1. the person playing domino is in an even position##4
2. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
3. the fan of funk is the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1
5. the fan of classical is the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Game   | backgammon | domino | mah-jongg |
| Music-Genre    | classical    | house | funk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
City: hamburg, new-york, edinburgh
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, german, british
1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far right##1
2. the german is in an even position##4
3. the british is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
4. the german is the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| City       | new-york | edinburgh | hamburg |
| Nationality   | british    | german     | nigerian        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, german, indian
There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, brown, lilac
1. the malaysian is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
2. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
3. the german is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Nationality         | indian     | german | malaysian |
| Color   | brown | pink     | lilac  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, coffee, almond-milk
City: colone, liverpool, rome
1. the person drinking coffee is the person traveling to liverpool##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is the person traveling to rome##1
3. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4
4. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | coffee  | mirinda  |
| City         | colone  | liverpool | rome |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
3 different games are played: backgammon, canasta, bridge
3 different pets are kept: dog, rabbit, hamster
1. the person playing bridge is between the person playing backgammon and the owner of the dog##2
2. the person playing canasta is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Game         | backgammon   | bridge | canasta    |
| Pet   | rabbit | hamster     | dog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, bellflower, rose
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, davidoff, game
1. the person who growslily is the davidoff-smoker##1
2. the game-smoker is the person who growsbellflower##1
3. the person who growsbellflower is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growsrose is on the right of the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Flower   | bellflower | rose | lily   |
| Cigar   | game     | baccarat    | davidoff |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, boat, helicopter
House: ranch-style, cape-cod, farmhouse
1. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the car is between the farmhouse house and the person driving the helicopter##2
3. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
4. the ranch-style house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Transport   | helicopter | car | boat |
| House           | cape-cod         | ranch-style         | farmhouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
