.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, superhero, animation
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, pakistani, japanese
1. the japanese is in an odd position##4
2. the pakistani is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
3. the japanese is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the japanese is on the left or right of the pakistani##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | animation   | superhero  | family  |
| Nationality         | japanese | pakistani | italian |

