The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, ambient, blues
1. the fan of punk is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
2. the fan of blues is in an even position##4
3. the fan of blues is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| City   | prague    | colone      | boston |
| Music-Genre       | ambient | blues | punk   |

