.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, grey, lavender
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, disaster, scientific
1. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
2. the person watching epic movies is the person who likes red##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is the person who likes lavender##1
4. the person who likes lavender is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Color         | grey | lavender | red |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | scientific   | epic |

