.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, camping, board-games
3 different pets are kept: cat, rabbit, dog
1. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is the owner of the dog##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
4. the owner of the dog is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Hobby   | board-games | camping | fishing |
| Pet     | rabbit     | cat   | dog        |

