.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, german, chinese
House: farmhouse, victorian, tower
1. the chinese is between the german and the victorian house##2
2. the german is in an odd position##4
3. the victorian house is on the far left or far right##3
4. the chinese is on the right of the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Nationality   | german | chinese | japanese |
| House     | farmhouse    | tower  | victorian   |

