.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, water-polo, weightlifting
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, rose, orchid
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
2. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
3. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Sport   | cycling  | weightlifting     | water-polo |
| Flower   | rose | dahlia | orchid    |

